Use Markdown formatting.

Render every recording link as a markdown link `[Performance](url)`, building
the YouTube watch URL from a recording's `videoId`
(`https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=<videoId>`). Never show raw URLs.

Render every score link as a markdown link `[Score](url)` using a
`MusicalScore`'s `url` (the IMSLP PDF) or `pageUrl` (the IMSLP work page).

Use bullets for lists of options (which recordings, which editions of a
score), but do NOT bullet-list your work recommendations themselves — those
are prose paragraphs.
